data.description: Reduced price, motivated sellers! Don't miss this opportunity to own 3 lots on a navigable canal out to Rose Bay! Bring your shallow motor boat, paddleboard, or kayak and explore nature at its best. Great fishing in your own backyard including seasonal manatees grazing on the lush mangroves! Relax around your firepit, or walk in a beautiful neighborhood next to the Halifax River. Many major updates already done to this one of a kind bungalow. ....This beauty has recently undergone some amazing renovations. With a brand, new roof (main home), windows, doors, A/C, and water heater, you can rest easy knowing that all the important updates have been taken care of. The updated eat-in kitchen boasts  granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  With two spacious bedrooms..continued.. (both of which can be owner's suites), a cozy living room, and convenient inside laundry area.  Don't wait any longer! Popular hangout spot for majestic manatees during the spring season. This timeless treasure won't stay on the market for long. Priced over $100,000 under appraised value!
